platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We love how language learning becomes a game  the irresistible kind anyone can pick up and play. Learn everyday words and phrases, and reinforce them with fun quizzes.

With Memrise, language learnings a gamethe irresistible kind that anyone can pick up and play. It teaches you everyday words and phrasesperfect for your next trip abroadand reinforces them with fun quizzes and playful images. We get an awesome sense of progress every time we use it.
Lapprentissage des langues devient un jeu irrsistible et accessible  tout le monde. Apprenez des mots et des phrases de tous les jours et consolidez-les avec des quiz amusants.
